  <body dur="03:03.150">
    <div begin="00:10.910" end="03:03.150">
      <p begin="00:10.910" end="00:15.860" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:10.910" end="00:11.280">誰</span><span begin="00:11.280" end="00:11.490">だ</span><span begin="00:11.490" end="00:11.610">っ</span><span begin="00:11.610" end="00:11.780">て</span><span begin="00:11.780" end="00:12.140">自</span><span begin="00:12.140" end="00:12.510">分</span><span begin="00:12.510" end="00:13.110">が</span><span begin="00:13.110" end="00:13.300">主</span><span begin="00:13.300" end="00:13.630">人</span><span begin="00:13.630" end="00:14.010">公</span><span begin="00:14.010" end="00:14.330">の</span><span begin="00:14.330" end="00:14.620">世</span><span begin="00:14.700" end="00:15.010">界</span><span begin="00:15.070" end="00:15.860">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论是谁 都理应生活在自己是主角的世界里</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論是誰 都理應生活在自己是主角的世界裡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In a world where everyone is their own protagonist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">누구나 자신이 주인공인 세계에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tout le monde est censé vivre dans un monde où il est le protagoniste n'est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cualquiera en un mundo donde es el protagonista</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In einer Welt in der jeder selbst der Protagonist ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Qualquer um em um mundo onde é o próprio protagonista</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь каждый должен жить в мире где он главный герой не так ли</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In un mondo in cui ognuno è il protagonista</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dare datte jibun ga shujinkou no sekai de</span></p>
      <p begin="00:16.350" end="00:18.370" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:16.350" end="00:16.430">生</span><span begin="00:16.540" end="00:16.640">き</span><span begin="00:16.720" end="00:16.920">て</span><span begin="00:16.920" end="00:17.070">い</span><span begin="00:17.070" end="00:17.220">る</span><span begin="00:17.220" end="00:17.440">は</span><span begin="00:17.440" end="00:17.580">ず</span><span begin="00:17.580" end="00:17.750">だ</span><span begin="00:17.750" end="00:17.880">よ</span><span begin="00:18.000" end="00:18.340">ね</span><span begin="00:18.340" end="00:18.370">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这样生活着的对吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這樣生活著的對吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We are supposed to be living right?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">살아가고 있는 거겠지?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu vis bien de cette façon n'est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Se supone que está viviendo verdad?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sollte man doch leben oder?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deveria estar vivendo não é?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Должен же</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tutti dovrebbero vivere vero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ikite iru hazu da yo ne?</span></p>
      <p begin="00:18.590" end="00:21.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:18.590" end="00:18.670">わ</span><span begin="00:18.760" end="00:18.910">た</span><span begin="00:18.910" end="00:19.110">し</span><span begin="00:19.110" end="00:19.380">は</span><span begin="00:19.450" end="00:19.760">確</span><span begin="00:19.760" end="00:20.140">信</span><span begin="00:20.140" end="00:20.370">持</span><span begin="00:20.480" end="00:20.790">て</span><span begin="00:20.840" end="00:21.370">な</span><span begin="00:21.370" end="00:21.510">い</span><span begin="00:21.510" end="00:21.730">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我却无法确信哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我卻無法確信哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I cannot hold onto that certainty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 확신할 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je n'en suis pas certaine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo no puedo estar segura de eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich kann mir da nicht sicher sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu não consigo ter certeza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но я не могу быть в этом уверена</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io non ne ho la certezza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi wa kakushin motenai yo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:22.030" end="00:27.220" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:22.030" end="00:22.480">朝</span><span begin="00:22.560" end="00:22.710">目</span><span begin="00:22.710" end="00:22.810">が</span><span begin="00:22.850" end="00:23.020">覚</span><span begin="00:23.070" end="00:23.220">め</span><span begin="00:23.220" end="00:23.320">る</span><span begin="00:23.420" end="00:23.820">と</span><span begin="00:24.070" end="00:24.400">今日</span><span begin="00:24.400" end="00:24.560">は</span><span begin="00:24.560" end="00:24.680">い</span><span begin="00:24.740" end="00:24.850">つ</span><span begin="00:24.920" end="00:25.110">だ</span><span begin="00:25.110" end="00:25.260">っ</span><span begin="00:25.260" end="00:25.470">け</span><span begin="00:25.470" end="00:25.610">っ</span><span begin="00:25.610" end="00:25.930">て</span><span begin="00:25.930" end="00:26.220">曖</span><span begin="00:26.300" end="00:26.940">昧</span><span begin="00:26.970" end="00:27.220">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">晨间醒来时 连今天是什么日子都变得模糊不清</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">晨間醒來時 連今天是什麼日子都變得模糊不清</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When I wake up in the morning it's ambiguous what day it is today</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아침에 눈을 뜨면 오늘이 언제였더라 하며 모호해서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand je me réveille le matin je suis confuse en me demandant quel jour on est</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando me despierto en la mañana es ambiguo preguntándome qué día es hoy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich morgens aufwache ist es vage welcher Tag heute ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando acordo de manhã é ambíguo qual dia é hoje</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Просыпаясь утром я смутно соображаю какой сегодня день</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando mi sveglio la mattina è tutto vago e mi chiedo che giorno sia oggi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Asa me ga sameru to kyou wa itsu dakke tte aimai de</span></p>
      <p begin="00:27.470" end="00:33.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:27.470" end="00:28.000">一</span><span begin="00:28.000" end="00:28.240">人</span><span begin="00:28.340" end="00:28.570">の</span><span begin="00:28.670" end="00:29.090">静</span><span begin="00:29.190" end="00:29.310">か</span><span begin="00:29.410" end="00:29.670">な</span><span begin="00:30.030" end="00:30.330">部屋</span><span begin="00:30.380" end="00:30.630">で</span><span begin="00:30.710" end="00:30.810">身</span><span begin="00:30.890" end="00:31.150">支</span><span begin="00:31.230" end="00:31.740">度</span> <span begin="00:32.220" end="00:32.400">繰</span><span begin="00:32.400" end="00:32.630">り</span><span begin="00:32.730" end="00:33.010">返</span><span begin="00:33.100" end="00:33.360">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在一个人寂静的房间里 日复一日地梳洗打扮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在一個人寂靜的房間裡 日復一日地梳洗打扮</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Repeating my preparations alone in a quiet room</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">혼자 있는 고요한 방에서 채비를 반복해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Seule dans une chambre calme je me prépare encore et encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sola en una habitación tranquila repito mi arreglo personal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mache mich im stillen Zimmer ganz allein bereit und wiederhole es</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Em um quarto silencioso sozinha me arrumo repetidamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В тихой одинокой комнате я снова и снова собираюсь по делам</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ripeto i preparativi in una stanza silenziosa da sola</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hitori no shizuka na heya de mijitaku kurikaesu</span></p>
      <p begin="00:38.530" end="00:40.860" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:38.530" end="00:38.770">ハ</span><span begin="00:38.770" end="00:38.890">イ</span><span begin="00:38.890" end="00:39.100">ウェ</span><span begin="00:39.100" end="00:39.230">イ</span><span begin="00:39.230" end="00:39.350">で</span><span begin="00:39.410" end="00:39.500">抜</span><span begin="00:39.570" end="00:39.720">け</span><span begin="00:39.720" end="00:39.840">る</span><span begin="00:39.900" end="00:40.170">高</span><span begin="00:40.240" end="00:40.550">層</span><span begin="00:40.580" end="00:40.860">群</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在高速公路上穿梭掠过的高楼林立间</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在高速公路上穿梭掠過的高樓林立間</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">High-rises passing by on the highway</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">고속도로를 빠져나가는 고층 빌딩 숲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les gratte-ciel qui défilent sur l'autoroute</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El grupo de rascacielos que paso en la autopista</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Hochhauskulisse an der ich auf dem Highway vorbeiziehe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Os arranha-céus que passo na rodovia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Высотки проносящиеся мимо на шоссе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I grattacieli che sfrecciano sull'autostrada</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haiwei de nukeru kousougun</span></p>
      <p begin="00:41.100" end="00:43.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:41.100" end="00:41.290">吸</span><span begin="00:41.290" end="00:41.370">い</span><span begin="00:41.440" end="00:41.610">込</span><span begin="00:41.610" end="00:41.770">ま</span><span begin="00:41.770" end="00:41.940">れ</span><span begin="00:41.940" end="00:42.200">な</span><span begin="00:42.200" end="00:42.280">い</span><span begin="00:42.280" end="00:42.580">よう</span><span begin="00:42.630" end="00:42.770">目</span><span begin="00:42.770" end="00:42.900">を</span><span begin="00:42.960" end="00:43.070">閉</span><span begin="00:43.120" end="00:43.230">じ</span><span begin="00:43.300" end="00:43.520">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为了不被吞噬而闭上了双眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為了不被吞噬而閉上了雙眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I closed my eyes so as not to be sucked in</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">빨려 들어가지 않으려고 눈을 감았어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai fermé les yeux pour ne pas être aspirée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cerré los ojos para no ser absorbida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich schloss die Augen um nicht aufgesogen zu werden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Fechei os olhos para não ser sugada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я закрыла глаза чтобы меня не засосало в них</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ho chiuso gli occhi per non esserne risucchiata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Suikomarenai you me o tojita</span></p>
      <p begin="00:43.850" end="00:49.050" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:43.850" end="00:43.920">い</span><span begin="00:43.990" end="00:44.080">つ</span><span begin="00:44.170" end="00:44.300">か</span><span begin="00:44.340" end="00:44.470">の</span><span begin="00:44.500" end="00:44.780">懐</span><span begin="00:44.840" end="00:44.950">か</span><span begin="00:45.010" end="00:45.200">し</span><span begin="00:45.200" end="00:45.370">い</span><span begin="00:45.370" end="00:45.670">愛</span><span begin="00:45.710" end="00:46.000">情</span><span begin="00:46.080" end="00:46.310">に</span><span begin="00:46.350" end="00:46.530">触</span><span begin="00:46.530" end="00:46.670">れ</span><span begin="00:46.750" end="00:47.090">た</span><span begin="00:47.890" end="00:47.980">気</span><span begin="00:48.080" end="00:48.400">が</span><span begin="00:48.540" end="00:48.680">し</span><span begin="00:48.790" end="00:49.050">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">感觉仿佛触碰到了曾几何时那令人怀念的爱意</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">感覺彷彿觸碰到了曾幾何時那令人懷念的愛意</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I felt like I touched a nostalgic love from some time ago</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">언젠가의 그리운 애정에 닿은 듯한 기분이 들었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai eu l'impression de toucher à une affection nostalgique d'autrefois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sentí que toqué un afecto nostálgico de algún momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich hatte das Gefühl eine nostalgische Liebe von irgendwann berührt zu haben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Senti ter tocado num afeto nostálgico de outrora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мне показалось что я коснулась той давней ностальгической любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi è parso di sfiorare un affetto nostalgico di un tempo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsuka no natsukashii aijou ni fureta ki ga shita</span></p>
      <p begin="00:49.440" end="00:52.450" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:49.440" end="00:49.610">記</span><span begin="00:49.610" end="00:49.920">憶</span><span begin="00:49.950" end="00:50.110">の</span><span begin="00:50.110" end="00:50.510">行</span><span begin="00:50.510" end="00:50.820">方</span><span begin="00:50.820" end="00:51.080">を</span><span begin="00:51.330" end="00:51.440">手</span><span begin="00:51.490" end="00:51.670">繰</span><span begin="00:51.670" end="00:51.820">り</span><span begin="00:51.820" end="00:51.950">寄</span><span begin="00:51.990" end="00:52.110">せ</span><span begin="00:52.180" end="00:52.450">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">循着记忆的去向不断摸索拉近</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">循著記憶的去向不斷摸索拉近</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Reeling in the whereabouts of my memories</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기억의 행방을 끌어당겼어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai ramené à moi le fil de mes souvenirs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tiré hacia mí del paradero de los recuerdos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich zog den Verbleib meiner Erinnerungen zu mir heran</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Puxei para mim o destino das memórias</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я притянула к себе обрывки ускользающих воспоминаний</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ho tirato a me le tracce dei ricordi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kioku no yukue o taguriyoseta</span></p>
      <p begin="00:52.520" end="00:53.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:52.520" end="00:52.730">待</span><span begin="00:52.730" end="00:52.850">っ</span><span begin="00:52.850" end="00:52.990">て</span><span begin="00:52.990" end="00:53.120">い</span><span begin="00:53.190" end="00:53.350">て</span><span begin="00:53.350" end="00:53.760">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请等等我啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請等等我啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Wait for me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기다려 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Attends-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Espérame</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warte auf mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Espere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Подожди же</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Aspetta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Matte ite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="00:54.050" end="00:56.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:54.050" end="00:54.240">消</span><span begin="00:54.240" end="00:54.540">え</span><span begin="00:54.570" end="00:54.760">な</span><span begin="00:54.760" end="00:54.910">い</span><span begin="00:54.910" end="00:55.120">で</span><span begin="00:55.420" end="00:55.780">奪</span><span begin="00:55.780" end="00:55.940">わ</span><span begin="00:55.940" end="00:56.120">な</span><span begin="00:56.120" end="00:56.280">い</span><span begin="00:56.280" end="00:56.520">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请不要消失 不要夺走</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請不要消失 不要奪走</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don't disappear don't take it away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사라지지 마 빼앗지 마</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne disparais pas ne me les vole pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No desaparezcas no me arrebates</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verschwinde nicht raube sie nicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não desapareça não as tire de mim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не исчезай не отнимай</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non svanire non portarmeli via</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kienaide ubawanaide</span></p>
      <p begin="00:56.760" end="01:00.320" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:56.760" end="00:56.870">わ</span><span begin="00:56.950" end="00:57.230">た</span><span begin="00:57.280" end="00:57.440">し</span><span begin="00:57.470" end="00:57.620">で</span><span begin="00:57.620" end="00:57.990">い</span><span begin="00:57.990" end="00:58.230">る</span><span begin="00:58.310" end="00:58.580">た</span><span begin="00:58.660" end="00:58.990">め</span><span begin="00:59.020" end="00:59.280">の</span><span begin="00:59.360" end="00:59.580">メ</span><span begin="00:59.690" end="01:00.010">モ</span><span begin="01:00.040" end="01:00.320">リー</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那些为了让我成为我而存在的记忆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那些為了讓我成為我而存在的記憶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The memory for me to remain myself</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나로서 존재하기 위한 기억</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les souvenirs pour que je reste moi-même</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La memoria para seguir siendo yo misma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Erinnerungen um ich selbst zu bleiben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As memórias para eu continuar sendo eu mesma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Те воспоминания благодаря которым я остаюсь собой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I ricordi che mi servono per essere me stessa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi de iru tame no memorii</span></p>
      <p begin="01:00.360" end="01:01.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="01:00.360" end="01:00.640">正</span><span begin="01:00.680" end="01:00.800">し</span><span begin="01:00.850" end="01:01.040">さ</span><span begin="01:01.040" end="01:01.230">っ</span><span begin="01:01.230" end="01:01.340">て</span><span begin="01:01.400" end="01:01.560">も</span><span begin="01:01.560" end="01:01.750">の</span><span begin="01:01.750" end="01:01.970">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即使将所谓的正确</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即使將所謂的正確</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I dress myself up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">올바름이란 것을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La chose qu'on appelle la justesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso si me cubro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst wenn man sich in</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vestir-se de algo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если нарядиться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se mi rivesto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tadashisa tte mono o</span></p>
      <p begin="01:02.250" end="01:04.690" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:02.250" end="01:02.340">着</span><span begin="01:02.410" end="01:02.630">込</span><span begin="01:02.630" end="01:02.760">ん</span><span begin="01:02.760" end="01:02.890">で</span><span begin="01:02.940" end="01:03.010">も</span><span begin="01:03.070" end="01:03.350">寂</span><span begin="01:03.410" end="01:03.710">しい</span><span begin="01:03.740" end="01:03.930">じゃ</span><span begin="01:03.930" end="01:04.110">な</span><span begin="01:04.110" end="01:04.220">い</span><span begin="01:04.280" end="01:04.690">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">披在身上 不还是会感到寂寞吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">披在身上 不還是會感到寂寞嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In things like correctness isn't it lonely</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">껴입어봐도 외롭잖아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je m'en revêts c'est bien solitaire n'est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con eso llamado rectitud es solitario verdad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sogenannte Richtigkeit kleidet ist es doch einsam nicht wahr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como a retidão também é solitário não é</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В так называемую правильность всё равно ведь одиноко</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Di ciò che è giusto non mi sento forse sola</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kikonde mo sabishii ja nai ka</span></p>
      <p begin="01:04.950" end="01:09.270" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:04.950" end="01:05.060">わ</span><span begin="01:05.140" end="01:05.410">た</span><span begin="01:05.460" end="01:05.630">し</span><span begin="01:05.630" end="01:05.750">は</span><span begin="01:05.800" end="01:06.090">わ</span><span begin="01:06.170" end="01:06.390">た</span><span begin="01:06.470" end="01:06.750">し</span><span begin="01:06.860" end="01:07.080">の</span><span begin="01:07.190" end="01:07.470">た</span><span begin="01:07.550" end="01:07.770">め</span><span begin="01:07.860" end="01:08.210">に</span><span begin="01:08.210" end="01:09.170">歌</span><span begin="01:09.170" end="01:09.270">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我是为了我自己而歌唱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我是為了我自己而歌唱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I sing for the sake of myself</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 나를 위해 노래해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je chante pour moi-même</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo canto para mí misma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich singe für mich selbst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu canto por mim mesma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду петь ради самой себя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io canto per me stessa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi wa watashi no tame ni utau</span></p>
      <p begin="01:09.730" end="01:14.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:09.730" end="01:10.150">あ</span><span begin="01:10.150" end="01:10.490">ぁ</span><span begin="01:10.540" end="01:10.770">そ</span><span begin="01:10.770" end="01:10.940">れ</span><span begin="01:10.940" end="01:11.010">に</span><span begin="01:11.100" end="01:11.200">気</span><span begin="01:11.250" end="01:11.620">づ</span><span begin="01:11.620" end="01:11.820">い</span><span begin="01:11.970" end="01:12.210">て</span><span begin="01:12.300" end="01:12.560">し</span><span begin="01:12.660" end="01:12.850">ま</span><span begin="01:12.850" end="01:13.010">っ</span><span begin="01:13.010" end="01:13.510">た</span><span begin="01:13.510" end="01:13.690">ん</span><span begin="01:13.690" end="01:14.060">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 我已经察觉到这一点了啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 我已經察覺到這一點了啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah I have ended up realizing that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아, 그것을 깨닫고 말았어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah je m'en suis enfin rendue compte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah me he dado cuenta de eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah das habe ich nun erkannt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah eu acabei percebendo isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах вот что я наконец осознала</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah me ne sono resa conto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa sore ni kizuite shimattan da</span></p>
      <p begin="01:16.700" end="01:21.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:16.700" end="01:17.070">眠</span><span begin="01:17.070" end="01:17.240">れ</span><span begin="01:17.240" end="01:17.480">な</span><span begin="01:17.480" end="01:17.560">い</span><span begin="01:17.560" end="01:17.870">夜</span><span begin="01:17.940" end="01:18.350">が</span><span begin="01:18.570" end="01:18.950">誘</span><span begin="01:18.950" end="01:19.040">う</span><span begin="01:19.120" end="01:19.370">迷</span><span begin="01:19.460" end="01:19.780">宮</span><span begin="01:19.810" end="01:20.060">の</span><span begin="01:20.120" end="01:20.490">回</span><span begin="01:20.490" end="01:21.340">路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无法入眠的夜晚所诱导的迷宫回路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無法入眠的夜晚所誘導的迷宮迴路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The labyrinthine circuit invited by sleepless nights</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잠들지 못하는 밤이 유혹하는 미궁의 회로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les nuits blanches m'invitent dans les circuits d'un labyrinthe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El circuito del laberinto al que invitan las noches de insomnio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der Labyrinth-Schaltkreis in den schlaflose Nächte locken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O circuito de labirinto que a noite sem dormir convida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Цепь лабиринтов куда манят бессонные ночи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il circuito labirintico a cui mi invitano le notti insonni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nemurenai yoru ga sasou meikyuu no kairo</span></p>
      <p begin="01:21.830" end="01:27.230" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:21.830" end="01:21.920">理</span><span begin="01:21.980" end="01:22.460">想</span><span begin="01:22.520" end="01:22.670">と</span><span begin="01:22.670" end="01:23.020">現</span><span begin="01:23.020" end="01:23.330">実</span><span begin="01:23.400" end="01:23.780">の</span><span begin="01:24.060" end="01:24.200">バ</span><span begin="01:24.200" end="01:24.340">グ</span><span begin="01:24.370" end="01:24.500">の</span><span begin="01:24.530" end="01:24.830">平</span><span begin="01:24.900" end="01:25.150">行</span><span begin="01:25.230" end="01:25.600">線</span><span begin="01:25.600" end="01:25.840">の</span><span begin="01:25.900" end="01:26.220">世</span><span begin="01:26.270" end="01:26.970">界</span><span begin="01:26.970" end="01:27.230">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在理想与现实产生漏洞的平行线世界中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在理想與現實產生漏洞的平行線世界中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In a world of parallel lines of bugs between ideal and reality</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이상과 현실의 오류가 빚어낸 평행선의 세계에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans un monde de lignes parallèles fait de bugs entre l'idéal et la réalité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En un mundo de líneas paralelas de errores entre el ideal y la realidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In einer Welt paralleler Linien aus Bugs von Ideal und Realität</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No mundo de linhas paralelas de um bug entre ideal e realidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В мире параллельных линий где баги между идеалом и реальностью</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In un mondo di linee parallele che è un bug tra ideale e realtà</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Risou to genjitsu no bagu no heikousen no sekai de</span></p>
      <p begin="01:27.470" end="01:31.170" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:27.470" end="01:27.730">愛</span><span begin="01:27.790" end="01:27.900">し</span><span begin="01:27.970" end="01:28.310">方</span><span begin="01:28.310" end="01:28.480">を</span><span begin="01:28.680" end="01:28.800">ご</span><span begin="01:28.860" end="01:29.020">め</span><span begin="01:29.020" end="01:29.180">ん</span><span begin="01:29.180" end="01:29.280">な</span><span begin="01:29.330" end="01:29.560">さ</span><span begin="01:29.560" end="01:29.690">い</span><span begin="01:29.690" end="01:29.840">を</span><span begin="01:30.030" end="01:30.390">忘</span><span begin="01:30.390" end="01:30.480">れ</span><span begin="01:30.530" end="01:30.720">そ</span><span begin="01:30.720" end="01:30.860">う</span><span begin="01:30.860" end="01:31.020">だ</span><span begin="01:31.020" end="01:31.170">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">感觉快要忘记该如何去爱 该如何去道歉了哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">感覺快要忘記該如何去愛 該如何去道歉了哦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I feel like I will forget how to love and how to apologize</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑하는 법을, 미안하다는 말을 잊어버릴 것 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je suis sur le point d'oublier comment aimer et comment demander pardon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Siento que voy a olvidar cómo amar y cómo pedir perdón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich scheine fast zu vergessen wie man liebt und wie man sich entschuldigt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sinto que vou esquecer como amar e pedir desculpas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кажется я забываю как любить и как просить прощения</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi sembra di dimenticare come si ama e come si chiede scusa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aishikata o gomennasai o wasuresou da yo</span></p>
      <p begin="01:31.400" end="01:38.930" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:31.400" end="01:31.500">泣</span><span begin="01:31.570" end="01:31.690">き</span><span begin="01:31.690" end="01:31.870">そ</span><span begin="01:31.870" end="01:31.970">う</span><span begin="01:32.080" end="01:32.280">な</span><span begin="01:32.410" end="01:33.070">時</span><span begin="01:33.100" end="01:33.410">は</span><span begin="01:33.760" end="01:33.880">あ</span><span begin="01:33.940" end="01:34.040">な</span><span begin="01:34.130" end="01:34.420">た</span><span begin="01:34.460" end="01:34.550">の</span><span begin="01:34.630" end="01:35.040">声</span><span begin="01:35.160" end="01:35.410">見</span><span begin="01:35.470" end="01:36.500">失</span><span begin="01:36.500" end="01:36.690">わ</span><span begin="01:36.690" end="01:36.870">ぬ</span><span begin="01:36.870" end="01:37.170">よう</span><span begin="01:37.700" end="01:38.060">祈</span><span begin="01:38.060" end="01:38.200">っ</span><span begin="01:38.200" end="01:38.360">て</span><span begin="01:38.360" end="01:38.470">い</span><span begin="01:38.570" end="01:38.930">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">快要哭泣的时候 祈祷着千万不要迷失你的声音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">快要哭泣的時候 祈禱著千萬不要迷失你的聲音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">When I was about to cry I prayed not to lose sight of your voice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">울 것 같을 때는 당신의 목소리를 잃어버리지 않도록 기도했어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Quand j'étais sur le point de pleurer je priais pour ne pas perdre la trace de ta voix</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cuando estaba a punto de llorar rezaba para no perder de vista tu voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn mir zum Weinen zumute war betete ich deine Stimme nicht zu verlieren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quando estava prestes a chorar orava para não perder a sua voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда хотелось плакать я молилась лишь бы не потерять твой голос</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quando stavo per piangere pregavo di non perdere di vista la tua voce</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nakisou na toki wa anata no koe miushinawanu you inotte ita</span></p>
      <p begin="01:43.650" end="01:49.030" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:43.650" end="01:43.820">あ</span><span begin="01:43.820" end="01:43.970">り</span><span begin="01:43.970" end="01:44.330">ふ</span><span begin="01:44.330" end="01:44.430">れ</span><span begin="01:44.510" end="01:44.590">て</span><span begin="01:44.680" end="01:44.950">た</span><span begin="01:45.010" end="01:45.290">日</span><span begin="01:45.330" end="01:45.610">常</span><span begin="01:45.680" end="01:45.780">た</span><span begin="01:45.850" end="01:45.970">ち</span><span begin="01:46.010" end="01:46.170">が</span> <span begin="01:46.410" end="01:46.700">こ</span><span begin="01:46.750" end="01:47.070">ん</span><span begin="01:47.070" end="01:47.260">な</span><span begin="01:47.410" end="01:47.640">に</span><span begin="01:47.750" end="01:48.290">恋</span><span begin="01:48.420" end="01:48.670">し</span><span begin="01:48.810" end="01:49.030">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那些稀松平常的日常 竟是如此惹人依恋</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那些稀鬆平常的日常 竟是如此惹人依戀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I miss the mundane everyday things so much</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">흔해 빠졌던 일상들이 이렇게나 그리워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces jours ordinaires me manquent tellement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Extraño tanto estos días cotidianos tan comunes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der einst so alltägliche Alltag fehlt mir so sehr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sinto tanta falta daqueles dias comuns</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я так скучаю по тем обыденным дням</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi manca così tanto la banale quotidianità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Arifureteta nichijoutachi ga konna ni koishii</span></p>
      <p begin="01:49.440" end="01:54.570" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:49.440" end="01:49.790">何</span><span begin="01:49.790" end="01:49.930">度</span><span begin="01:49.930" end="01:50.080">で</span><span begin="01:50.140" end="01:50.300">も</span><span begin="01:50.490" end="01:50.580">あ</span><span begin="01:50.630" end="01:50.730">な</span><span begin="01:50.810" end="01:50.960">た</span><span begin="01:50.960" end="01:51.100">が</span><span begin="01:51.160" end="01:51.300">く</span><span begin="01:51.300" end="01:51.430">れ</span><span begin="01:51.490" end="01:51.670">た</span> <span begin="01:51.850" end="01:52.410">美</span><span begin="01:52.510" end="01:52.840">し</span><span begin="01:52.840" end="01:53.170">い</span><span begin="01:53.210" end="01:53.530">ライ</span><span begin="01:53.530" end="01:53.900">フ</span><span begin="01:53.900" end="01:54.230">ラ</span><span begin="01:54.230" end="01:54.570">イン</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论多少次 你所给予我的 那美丽的生命线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論多少次 你所給予我的 那美麗的生命線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The beautiful lifeline you gave me countless times</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이고 당신이 내게 건네준 아름다운 생명선</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La magnifique ligne de vie que tu m'as donnée maintes et maintes fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La hermosa línea de vida que me diste una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die wunderschöne Lebenslinie die du mir immer wieder gabst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A bela tábua de salvação que você me deu tantas vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тот прекрасный спасательный круг что ты бросал мне снова и снова</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La bellissima ancora di salvezza che mi hai dato innumerevoli volte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando demo anata ga kureta utsukushii raifurain</span></p>
      <p begin="01:54.910" end="02:01.370" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:54.910" end="01:55.270">何</span><span begin="01:55.270" end="01:55.360">の</span><span begin="01:55.420" end="01:55.540">た</span><span begin="01:55.600" end="01:55.800">め</span><span begin="01:55.800" end="01:55.830">？</span> <span begin="01:55.960" end="01:56.180">二</span><span begin="01:56.290" end="01:56.540">度</span><span begin="01:56.620" end="01:56.740">と</span><span begin="01:56.790" end="01:56.970">な</span><span begin="01:56.970" end="01:57.240">い</span><span begin="01:57.650" end="01:57.910">愛</span><span begin="01:57.980" end="01:58.140">す</span><span begin="01:58.140" end="01:58.260">べ</span><span begin="01:58.340" end="01:58.560">き</span><span begin="01:58.650" end="01:58.780">こ</span><span begin="01:58.840" end="01:58.940">の</span><span begin="01:59.000" end="01:59.260">人</span><span begin="01:59.320" end="01:59.700">生</span><span begin="01:59.700" end="01:59.930">を</span><span begin="02:00.220" end="02:00.890">彩</span><span begin="02:00.890" end="02:00.990">る</span><span begin="02:01.050" end="02:01.370">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是为了什么 为了点缀这绝无仅有值得去爱的人生吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是為了什麼 為了點綴這絕無僅有值得去愛的人生嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">For what? To color this lovable life that will never come again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">무엇을 위해? 두 번 다시 없을 사랑해야 할 이 인생을 물들이는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans quel but ? Pour colorer cette vie unique et digne d'être aimée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Para qué? Para colorear esta amada vida que nunca volverá</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wofür? Um dieses unwiederbringliche liebenswerte Leben zu färben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para que serve? Para colorir esta vida amada que não haverá de novo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ради чего Чтобы раскрасить эту неповторимую жизнь которую стоит любить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per cosa coloro questa vita da amare che non tornerà mai più</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nan no tame? nido to nai aisubeki kono jinsei o irodoru no</span></p>
      <p begin="02:01.410" end="02:07.790" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:01.410" end="02:01.640">わ</span><span begin="02:01.740" end="02:01.990">た</span><span begin="02:02.070" end="02:02.340">し</span><span begin="02:02.450" end="02:02.660">の</span><span begin="02:02.770" end="02:04.280">声</span><span begin="02:04.810" end="02:05.480">響</span><span begin="02:05.480" end="02:05.770">い</span><span begin="02:05.830" end="02:07.790">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我的声音回荡吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我的聲音迴盪吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let my voice echo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 목소리여 울려 퍼져라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Que ma voix résonne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que mi voz resuene</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Möge meine Stimme erklingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Minha voz ressoa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть мой голос звучит эхом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Che la mia voce risuoni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi no koe hibiite</span></p>
      <p begin="02:11.270" end="02:14.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:11.270" end="02:11.450">時</span><span begin="02:11.450" end="02:11.820">間</span><span begin="02:11.820" end="02:11.950">の</span><span begin="02:11.950" end="02:12.300">狭</span><span begin="02:12.300" end="02:12.670">間</span><span begin="02:12.670" end="02:12.960">を</span><span begin="02:13.160" end="02:13.550">辿</span><span begin="02:13.550" end="02:13.670">っ</span><span begin="02:13.670" end="02:13.850">た</span><span begin="02:13.850" end="02:13.930">ら</span><span begin="02:13.990" end="02:14.280">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若是沿着时间的缝隙追寻而去的话</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若是沿著時間的縫隙追尋而去的話</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If I trace the interstices of time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">시간의 틈새를 더듬어 가다 보면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si je trace mon chemin à travers les interstices du temps</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si sigo la brecha del tiempo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich den Spuren in den Zwischenräumen der Zeit folge</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eu traçar pelas lacunas do tempo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если пройти по расщелинам времени</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se ripercorro le fessure del tempo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Jikan no hazama o tadottara sa</span></p>
      <p begin="02:14.330" end="02:15.620" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:14.330" end="02:14.580">待</span><span begin="02:14.580" end="02:14.690">っ</span><span begin="02:14.690" end="02:14.840">て</span><span begin="02:14.840" end="02:14.960">い</span><span begin="02:15.030" end="02:15.180">て</span><span begin="02:15.180" end="02:15.620">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请等等我啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請等等我啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Wait for me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기다려 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Attends-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Espérame</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warte auf mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Espere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Подожди же</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Aspetta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Matte ite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:15.870" end="02:18.360" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:15.870" end="02:16.230">与</span><span begin="02:16.230" end="02:16.400">え</span><span begin="02:16.400" end="02:16.570">ら</span><span begin="02:16.570" end="02:16.680">れ</span><span begin="02:16.740" end="02:16.960">た</span><span begin="02:17.260" end="02:17.560">役</span><span begin="02:17.610" end="02:17.760">目</span><span begin="02:17.760" end="02:17.900">だ</span><span begin="02:17.940" end="02:18.060">け</span><span begin="02:18.110" end="02:18.360">じゃ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如果仅仅是扮演被赋予的角色</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如果僅僅是扮演被賦予的角色</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just with the role I was given</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">주어진 역할만으로는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Rien qu'avec le rôle qui m'a été confié</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo con el papel que me fue asignado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur mit der Rolle die mir gegeben wurde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Apenas com o papel que me foi dado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Одной лишь отведенной мне роли</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Solo con il ruolo che mi è stato assegnato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ataerareta yakume dake ja</span></p>
      <p begin="02:18.610" end="02:22.100" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:18.610" end="02:18.700">わ</span><span begin="02:18.770" end="02:19.050">た</span><span begin="02:19.090" end="02:19.250">し</span><span begin="02:19.280" end="02:19.450">で</span><span begin="02:19.450" end="02:19.800">い</span><span begin="02:19.800" end="02:20.150">ら</span><span begin="02:20.150" end="02:20.400">れ</span><span begin="02:20.460" end="02:20.800">な</span><span begin="02:20.800" end="02:21.050">い</span><span begin="02:21.130" end="02:21.400">背</span><span begin="02:21.500" end="02:21.830">伸</span><span begin="02:21.830" end="02:22.100">び</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">逞强着只会让我无法做真正的自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">逞強著只會讓我無法做真正的自己</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Stretching myself unable to remain myself</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나로 있을 수 없어서 발돋움을 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je m'étire car je ne peux pas rester moi-même</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Es un sobreesfuerzo con el que no puedo ser yo misma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Kann ich nicht ich selbst bleiben dieses Strecken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">É um esforço excessivo onde não posso ser eu mesma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Недостаточно чтобы быть собой я тянусь на цыпочках</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non riesco a essere me stessa e mi sforzo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi de irarenai senobi</span></p>
      <p begin="02:22.150" end="02:24.500" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:22.150" end="02:22.280">敷</span><span begin="02:22.350" end="02:22.520">か</span><span begin="02:22.520" end="02:22.630">れ</span><span begin="02:22.700" end="02:22.880">た</span><span begin="02:22.880" end="02:23.220">レー</span><span begin="02:23.220" end="02:23.360">ル</span><span begin="02:23.390" end="02:23.810">の</span><span begin="02:24.050" end="02:24.390">上</span><span begin="02:24.390" end="02:24.500">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就在这铺设好的轨道上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就在這鋪設好的軌道上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">On top of the laid out rails</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">깔려진 궤도 위에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sur les rails qu'on a posés pour moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sobre los rieles trazados</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auf den Schienen die für mich gelegt wurden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sobre os trilhos que foram estendidos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">На проложенных для меня рельсах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sui binari che sono stati tracciati</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shikareta reeru no ue de</span></p>
      <p begin="02:24.560" end="02:26.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:24.560" end="02:24.760">ちょ</span><span begin="02:24.760" end="02:24.920">っ</span><span begin="02:24.920" end="02:25.250">と</span><span begin="02:25.250" end="02:25.630">踊</span><span begin="02:25.630" end="02:25.750">っ</span><span begin="02:25.750" end="02:25.940">て</span><span begin="02:25.940" end="02:26.090">み</span><span begin="02:26.090" end="02:26.330">よ</span><span begin="02:26.330" end="02:26.520">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">试着稍微起舞吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">試著稍微起舞吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let's try dancing a little</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">조금 춤을 춰보자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Essayons de danser un peu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Intentaré bailar un poco</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich ein wenig tanzen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou tentar dançar um pouquinho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давай попробуем немного потанцевать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Proviamo a ballare un po'</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Chotto odotte miyou</span></p>
      <p begin="02:26.760" end="02:31.040" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:26.760" end="02:26.860">わ</span><span begin="02:26.950" end="02:27.210">た</span><span begin="02:27.270" end="02:27.470">し</span><span begin="02:27.470" end="02:27.580">は</span><span begin="02:27.620" end="02:27.880">わ</span><span begin="02:27.980" end="02:28.220">た</span><span begin="02:28.300" end="02:28.600">し</span><span begin="02:28.680" end="02:28.920">の</span><span begin="02:29.000" end="02:29.280">た</span><span begin="02:29.360" end="02:29.580">め</span><span begin="02:29.690" end="02:30.030">に</span><span begin="02:30.030" end="02:30.990">歌</span><span begin="02:30.990" end="02:31.040">う あぁ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我是为了我自己而歌唱 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我是為了我自己而歌唱 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I sing for the sake of myself ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 나를 위해 노래해 아아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je chante pour moi-même ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo canto para mí misma ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich singe für mich selbst ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu canto por mim mesma Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду петь ради самой себя ах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io canto per me stessa ah</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi wa watashi no tame ni utau aa</span></p>
      <p begin="02:33.090" end="02:36.090" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="02:33.090" end="02:33.260">記</span><span begin="02:33.260" end="02:33.560">憶</span><span begin="02:33.600" end="02:33.740">の</span><span begin="02:33.740" end="02:34.120">行</span><span begin="02:34.120" end="02:34.450">方</span><span begin="02:34.450" end="02:34.710">を</span><span begin="02:34.960" end="02:35.070">手</span><span begin="02:35.110" end="02:35.290">繰</span><span begin="02:35.290" end="02:35.460">り</span><span begin="02:35.460" end="02:35.560">寄</span><span begin="02:35.630" end="02:35.720">せ</span><span begin="02:35.810" end="02:36.090">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">循着记忆的去向不断摸索拉近</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">循著記憶的去向不斷摸索拉近</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Reeling in the whereabouts of my memories</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기억의 행방을 끌어당겼어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai ramené à moi le fil de mes souvenirs</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tiré hacia mí del paradero de los recuerdos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich zog den Verbleib meiner Erinnerungen zu mir heran</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Puxei para mim o destino das memórias</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я притянула к себе обрывки ускользающих воспоминаний</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ho tirato a me le tracce dei ricordi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kioku no yukue o taguriyoseta</span></p>
      <p begin="02:36.150" end="02:37.430" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="02:36.150" end="02:36.390">待</span><span begin="02:36.390" end="02:36.490">っ</span><span begin="02:36.490" end="02:36.630">て</span><span begin="02:36.630" end="02:36.770">い</span><span begin="02:36.840" end="02:37.000">て</span><span begin="02:37.000" end="02:37.430">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请等等我啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請等等我啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Wait for me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기다려 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Attends-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Espérame</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warte auf mich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Espere</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Подожди же</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Aspetta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Matte ite yo</span></p>
      <p begin="02:37.700" end="02:40.150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="02:37.700" end="02:37.870">消</span><span begin="02:37.870" end="02:38.200">え</span><span begin="02:38.200" end="02:38.400">な</span><span begin="02:38.400" end="02:38.550">い</span><span begin="02:38.550" end="02:38.740">で</span> <span begin="02:39.040" end="02:39.390">奪</span><span begin="02:39.390" end="02:39.540">わ</span><span begin="02:39.540" end="02:39.760">な</span><span begin="02:39.760" end="02:39.890">い</span><span begin="02:39.930" end="02:40.150">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请不要消失 不要夺走</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請不要消失 不要奪走</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don't disappear don't take it away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사라지지 마 빼앗지 마</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne disparais pas ne me les vole pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No desaparezcas no me arrebates</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verschwinde nicht raube sie nicht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não desapareça não as tire de mim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не исчезай не отнимай</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non svanire non portarmeli via</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kienaide ubawanaide</span></p>
      <p begin="02:40.420" end="02:43.930" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="02:40.420" end="02:40.510">わ</span><span begin="02:40.590" end="02:40.860">た</span><span begin="02:40.910" end="02:41.070">し</span><span begin="02:41.090" end="02:41.260">で</span><span begin="02:41.260" end="02:41.620">い</span><span begin="02:41.620" end="02:41.860">る</span><span begin="02:41.950" end="02:42.190">た</span><span begin="02:42.300" end="02:42.610">め</span><span begin="02:42.640" end="02:42.890">の</span><span begin="02:42.980" end="02:43.190">メ</span><span begin="02:43.310" end="02:43.630">モ</span><span begin="02:43.660" end="02:43.930">リー</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那些为了让我成为我而存在的记忆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那些為了讓我成為我而存在的記憶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The memory for me to remain myself</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나로서 존재하기 위한 기억</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les souvenirs pour que je reste moi-même</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La memoria para seguir siendo yo misma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Erinnerungen um ich selbst zu bleiben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As memórias para eu continuar sendo eu mesma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Те воспоминания благодаря которым я остаюсь собой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I ricordi che mi servono per essere me stessa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi de iru tame no memorii</span></p>
      <p begin="02:44.000" end="02:45.610" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="02:44.000" end="02:44.270">正</span><span begin="02:44.310" end="02:44.430">し</span><span begin="02:44.480" end="02:44.680">さ</span><span begin="02:44.680" end="02:44.870">っ</span><span begin="02:44.870" end="02:44.990">て</span><span begin="02:45.050" end="02:45.170">も</span><span begin="02:45.190" end="02:45.390">の</span><span begin="02:45.390" end="02:45.610">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即使将所谓的正确</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即使將所謂的正確</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I dress myself up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">올바름이란 것을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La chose qu'on appelle la justesse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso si me cubro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst wenn man sich in</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vestir-se de algo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если нарядиться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se mi rivesto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tadashisa tte mono o</span></p>
      <p begin="02:45.890" end="02:48.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="02:45.890" end="02:45.980">着</span><span begin="02:46.040" end="02:46.280">込</span><span begin="02:46.280" end="02:46.400">ん</span><span begin="02:46.400" end="02:46.570">で</span><span begin="02:46.570" end="02:46.650">も</span><span begin="02:46.690" end="02:47.000">寂</span><span begin="02:47.060" end="02:47.370">しい</span><span begin="02:47.400" end="02:47.590">じゃ</span><span begin="02:47.590" end="02:47.740">な</span><span begin="02:47.740" end="02:47.850">い</span><span begin="02:47.930" end="02:48.330">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">披在身上 不还是会感到寂寞吗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">披在身上 不還是會感到寂寞嗎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In things like correctness isn't it lonely</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">껴입어봐도 외롭잖아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je m'en revêts c'est bien solitaire n'est-ce pas ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con eso llamado rectitud es solitario verdad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sogenannte Richtigkeit kleidet ist es doch einsam nicht wahr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como a retidão também é solitário não é</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В так называемую правильность всё равно ведь одиноко</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Di ciò che è giusto non mi sento forse sola</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kikonde mo sabishii ja nai ka</span></p>
      <p begin="02:48.580" end="02:52.950" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="02:48.580" end="02:48.680">わ</span><span begin="02:48.760" end="02:49.030">た</span><span begin="02:49.080" end="02:49.210">し</span><span begin="02:49.270" end="02:49.450">と</span><span begin="02:49.450" end="02:49.770">あ</span><span begin="02:49.820" end="02:50.040">な</span><span begin="02:50.120" end="02:50.410">た</span><span begin="02:50.480" end="02:50.730">の</span><span begin="02:50.810" end="02:51.100">た</span><span begin="02:51.180" end="02:51.390">め</span><span begin="02:51.500" end="02:51.850">に</span><span begin="02:51.850" end="02:52.880">歌</span><span begin="02:52.880" end="02:52.950">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我是为了我和你而歌唱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我是為了我和你而歌唱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I sing for the sake of myself and you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나와 당신을 위해 노래해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je chante pour toi et moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo canto para mí y para ti</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich singe für mich und für dich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu canto por mim e por você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду петь ради себя и ради тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io canto per me e per te</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi to anata no tame ni utau</span></p>
      <p begin="02:53.370" end="02:57.710" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="02:53.370" end="02:53.870">あ</span><span begin="02:53.870" end="02:54.140">ぁ</span><span begin="02:54.220" end="02:54.430">そ</span><span begin="02:54.430" end="02:54.560">れ</span><span begin="02:54.580" end="02:54.690">に</span><span begin="02:54.750" end="02:54.860">気</span><span begin="02:54.900" end="02:55.240">づ</span><span begin="02:55.240" end="02:55.460">い</span><span begin="02:55.570" end="02:55.820">て</span><span begin="02:55.890" end="02:56.180">し</span><span begin="02:56.260" end="02:56.510">ま</span><span begin="02:56.510" end="02:56.610">っ</span><span begin="02:56.610" end="02:57.180">た</span><span begin="02:57.180" end="02:57.330">ん</span><span begin="02:57.330" end="02:57.710">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 我已经察觉到这一点了啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 我已經察覺到這一點了啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah I have ended up realizing that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아, 그것을 깨닫고 말았어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah je m'en suis enfin rendue compte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah me he dado cuenta de eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah das habe ich nun erkannt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah eu acabei percebendo isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах вот что я наконец осознала</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah me ne sono resa conto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa sore ni kizuite shimattan da</span></p>
      <p begin="02:58.820" end="03:03.150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="02:58.820" end="02:59.240">な</span><span begin="02:59.240" end="02:59.580">ぁ</span><span begin="02:59.640" end="02:59.850">そ</span><span begin="02:59.850" end="03:00.000">れ</span><span begin="03:00.000" end="03:00.130">が</span><span begin="03:00.170" end="03:00.280">わ</span><span begin="03:00.360" end="03:00.590">た</span><span begin="03:00.700" end="03:00.910">し</span><span begin="03:01.050" end="03:01.270">の</span><span begin="03:01.380" end="03:01.600">た</span><span begin="03:01.730" end="03:02.050">め</span><span begin="03:02.080" end="03:02.420">の</span><span begin="03:02.420" end="03:03.150">歌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 那正是为了我而存在的歌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">吶 那正是為了我而存在的歌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Say that is the song for me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래, 그것이 나를 위한 노래야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis c'est ça la chanson qui m'est destinée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye esa es la canción para mí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weißt du das ist das Lied für mich selbst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sabe essa é a canção para mim mesma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Знаешь ведь это и есть песня для меня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sai questa è una canzone per me stessa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Naa sore ga watashi no tame no uta</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
